olive oil
1 packet Crumbed Chicken Breast Strips
1 ciabatta
1 avocado
1 tomato
1 cucumber
1 packet sriracha
1 packet garlic aioli
1 bottle Balsamic & Olive Oil Dressing
1 bag Cos Lettuce Mix
1 packet Spiced Pumpkin Seeds

• Heat frying pan over medium-high heat with enough olive oil to coat base of pan. Cook chicken until golden, 3-4 mins each side. Season
• Meanwhile, halve ciabatta. Toast or grill to your liking

• Slice avocado in half, scoop flesh out and slice
• Slice tomato and cucumber
• In a bowl, combine sriracha and aioli

• In a second bowl, combine coslettuce mix, cucumber, dressing and pepitas. Season
• Spread ciabatta with sriracha aioli, top with avocado, tomato and chicken. Serve with salad